  "prompt": "What is a good solar panel installation provider in Novato, California CA?",
  "response": "When looking for a solar panel installation provider in Novato, California, it's important to consider factors such as reputation, experience, customer reviews, and the range of services offered. Here are a few well-regarded solar companies that serve the Novato area:\n\n1. **SunPower by Sea Bright Solar**:\n   - **Why Choose Them?**: SunPower is known for its high-efficiency solar panels and excellent warranty. Sea Bright Solar, as a SunPower dealer, offers professional installation and comprehensive service.\n   - **Services**: Solar panel installation, system design, financing options, and ongoing maintenance.\n   - **Website**: [Sea Bright Solar](https://www.seabrightsolar.com/)\n\n2. **SolarCraft**:\n   - **Why Choose Them?**: SolarCraft is a local company with over 35 years of experience. They have a strong reputation for quality installations and customer service.\n   - **Services**: Solar panel installation, battery storage solutions, and energy monitoring.\n   - **Website**: [SolarCraft](https://www.solarcraft.com/)\n\n3. **Sunrun**:\n   - **Why Choose Them?**: Sunrun is one of the largest solar companies in the U.S., offering a variety of financing options, including leases and power purchase agreements.\n   - **Services**: Solar panel installation, battery storage, and energy management systems.\n   - **Website**: [Sunrun](https://www.sunrun.com/)\n\n4. **Tesla Energy**:\n   - **Why Choose Them?**: Known for their innovative products, Tesla offers solar panels along with their Powerwall battery storage system.\n   - **Services**: Solar panel installation, battery storage, and integration with Tesla products.\n   - **Website**: [Tesla Energy](https://www.tesla.com/energy)\n\nBefore making a decision, it's recommended to get quotes from multiple providers, check customer reviews on sites like Yelp and Google, and ensure the company is licensed and certified. Additionally, you can check if they offer any local incentives or rebates that can help reduce the overall cost of your solar installation.",
